* Simple Tone Control Circuit - Low-pass and High-pass filters

* Voltage source (AC input signal)
V1 N1 0 DC 0V AC 1V

* High-pass filter (Bass control)
R1 N1 N2 10k
C1 N2 0 100n

* Low-pass filter (Treble control)
R2 N2 N3 10k
C2 N3 0 100n

* Output signal
V2 N3 0 DC 0V AC 1V

* Grounding the circuit
.tran 1ms 10ms
.end
